data.description: Bring your boat to this Paradise Moorings treasure!!  Rock your cares away on the front porch, stroll the sidewalks lined with white picket fences in a gated Norman Rockwell setting.  The bright open floor plan boasts designer tile, hardwood floors, crown molding, wainscot in the Dining Room, French doors in the Living Room/Study.  The kitchen is the heart of the home with stainless appliances, and a large island that overlooks the Family Room.  Relax on the 800+ sf Florida Room, insulated, heated and cooled for year round comfort (not included in overall sq ft) Also features an upstairs 4th BR/bonus (new carpet)  w/ full bath.  Walk to the neighborhood dock and watch spectacular sunsets, or launch your boat on the private boat ramp and cruise Doctor's Lake.
